{
  "stem": "17426.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked at him and I said to myself, if I refuse, there's no one else here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what he'll do to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But I still don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only excusing myself that life is precious, and I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took a little box that one of the foremen made for me and kept separate instruments for that purpose.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I hope you would spare me to describe what I have gone through when I went to the dead room to extract gold from the teeth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But those that are interested in knowing, I broadly wrote about it in my book, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It is difficult.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It is sometime even difficult to bring it to your memory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not to say, how difficult it is to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I hope you spare me that, Louise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, we were in Furstengrube.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in time, they transferred all the doctors to the Front, because of so many German doctors were killed on the East Front, on the Russian Front.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had so many in their field [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] hospitals, that they needed every dentist and every doctor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was ordered to take care of the guards as well as the inmates.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was another shot in the arm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because when they came to a dentist, perhaps the fear for the dentist, perhaps of-- out of loyalty, or-- or maybe even at that time, the war wasn't going that great for them, perhaps there was a thought of losing the war, they brought me something to eat.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Food.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little I asked for it each time that the dentist came, but he brought me a few carpules and a few ampules of Novocain.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
